  <Docs>
    <summary><span data-ttu-id="509f9-101">将包含句柄的托管对象包装到通过平台调用传递到非托管代码的资源中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-101">Wraps a managed object holding a handle to a resource that is passed to unmanaged code using platform invoke.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="509f9-102">从 .NET Framework 2.0 开始，<xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> 类的功能已被 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle> 类及其派生类以及 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.CriticalHandle> 类所取代。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-102">Starting with the .NET Framework 2.0, the functionality of the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> class has been replaced by the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle> class and its derived classes, as well as by the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.CriticalHandle> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="509f9-103">如果你使用平台调用来调用托管对象，并且在平台调用调用后不会在其他位置引用该对象，则垃圾回收器可能会完成托管对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-103">If you use platform invoke to call a managed object, and the object is not referenced elsewhere after the platform invoke call, it is possible for the garbage collector to finalize the managed object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="509f9-104">此操作将释放资源并使句柄无效，从而导致平台调用失败。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-104">This action releases the resource and invalidates the handle, causing the platform invoke call to fail.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="509f9-105">使用 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> 包装句柄可保证在平台调用完成之前不会对托管对象进行垃圾回收。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-105">Wrapping a handle with <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> guarantees that the managed object is not garbage collected until the platform invoke call completes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="509f9-106">有关平台调用服务的说明，请参阅[使用非托管 DLL 函数](~/docs/framework/interop/consuming-unmanaged-dll-functions.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-106">For a description of platform invoke services, see [Consuming Unmanaged DLL Functions](~/docs/framework/interop/consuming-unmanaged-dll-functions.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="509f9-107"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> 值类型（如 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.GCHandle>）是互操作封送拆收器识别的特殊类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-107">The <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> value type, like <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.GCHandle>, is a special type recognized by the interop marshaler.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="509f9-108">正常的 nonpinned <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.GCHandle> 也会阻止不当垃圾回收，但 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> 提供更好的性能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-108">A normal, nonpinned <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.GCHandle> also prevents untimely garbage collection, yet <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> provides better performance.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="509f9-109">尽管使用 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> 在平台调用的持续时间内保持对象处于活动状态，但也可以将 <xref:System.GC.KeepAlive%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 方法用于相同的目的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-109">Although using <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> to keep an object alive for the duration of a platform invoke call is preferred, you can also use the <xref:System.GC.KeepAlive%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method for the same purpose.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="509f9-110"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> 构造函数采用两个参数：表示包装的 <xref:System.Object>，以及表示非托管句柄的 <xref:System.IntPtr>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-110">The <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.HandleRef> constructor takes two parameters: an <xref:System.Object> representing the wrapper, and an <xref:System.IntPtr> representing the unmanaged handle.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="509f9-111">互操作封送拆收器仅将句柄传递给非托管代码，并保证包装（作为第一个参数传递给 `HandleRef`的构造函数）在调用期间保持活动状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="509f9-111">The interop marshaler passes only the handle to unmanaged code, and guarantees that the wrapper (passed as the first parameter to the constructor of the `HandleRef`) remains alive for the duration of the call.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
